{"tid":255259,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【世紀預言】89年《再見王老五》預示「終極劏房」成真","createTime":"2017-05-23T19:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T11:21:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"801669ca8541215864ddeb93926c5372a5ec138f","tid":255259,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2016/12/07/9/9499ecbbc6d22ae611f8d4e5c3dc5d78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F9%2F9499ecbbc6d22ae611f8d4e5c3dc5d78.jpg&h=b3c1a3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SYjWRfqGhm0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSYjWRfqGhm0&d=u8WlpgPihxyMZGT20wMdJjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=8f0c8173\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SYjWRfqGhm0</a><br />\n早前有地產商推出史上最細的128呎屯門新盤，令全城嘩然，更被稱為「終極劏房」；發展商稱絕細單位是參考學生宿舍設計，又謂「皇帝都係瞓張床」令人啼笑皆非。<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：屯門菁雋開放式 最細128呎<br />\n<br />\n令人嘖嘖稱奇的是，早在1989年的電影《再見王老五》中，已預示了「終極劏房」的出現，片中地產經紀帶同鍾鎮濤與張曼玉睇樓，參觀的正是「終極劏房」超迷你單位。當中鍾鎮濤不斷投訴單位太細、放不下傢俱電器等，睡房更只能放下一張床！而片中地產經紀的詭辯亦是似曾相識：「市中心二千八蚊租去邊度搵丫」「擺唔到傢俬咪啱，擺唔到可以買少啲，買少啲可以慳多啲」「隱閉式餐檯，可以享受二人世界」「(因廁所太細，被質疑一開花灑馬桶便會濕透) 無人大便嘅時候開花灑架係咪？」<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：128呎單位設開放式廚房設備齊全<br />\n<br />\n電影橋段雖然好笑，但在30年後的今日，荒謬的電影情節成為了現實，相信很多人都笑不出來；更有網民表示：「最慘係，我覺得真係算接受到，如果宜家二千八，抵到爛」"},{"pid":"86a293026d37e5fccaac391c42479523fe99890c","tid":255259,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:03:19.000Z","msg":"有線呢排成日播"},{"pid":"f82d325b438693f496cad3ca9112fe30f6b19a9a","tid":255259,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b964dc0c6c47194ab1e83bf89deee51680f236","tid":255259,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4566add73e2ddd343ad1e5ac3c8cf5f488c16c","tid":255259,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99434173ab2899da98f3e580d905a9ec6a4b4b4","tid":255259,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8faaeb5b52ca1cd64492aca5cd8263a591800553","tid":255259,"uid":25641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d5190d54eeba8eb678bacee3d1298254eab0326","tid":255259,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T11:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}